  "remarks": "Associated with the Organization of Al-Qaida in the Islamic Maghreb (QDE.014), Ansar al-Shari’a in Tunisia (AAS-T) (QDE.143) and Ansar al Charia Benghazi (QDE.146). Runs training camps for foreign terrorist fighters travelling to Syria and Iraq. Review pursuant to Security Council resolution 2368 (2017) was concluded on 4 Dec. 2019. INTERPOL-UN Security Council Special Notice web link: https://www.interpol.int/en/How-we-work/Notices/View-UN-Notices-Entities.",
